ruleModal.title: Rules of play
ruleModal.list01: An account can only accept one investment before exiting, and can continue to invest after exiting
ruleModal.list02: Static dividends fluctuate from 0.3% to 2.2% per day
ruleModal.list03: Out of the game, according to 1-10 for the investment amount of 3 times, 11-30 for the investment amount of 4 times, greater than 31 for the investment amount of 5 times
ruleModal.list04: Dynamic recommendation 25% according to: 10%->8%->7% to get dynamic rewards, instant cash withdrawal
ruleModal.list05: After the prize pool reaches the specified time, the prize pool will not settle until the next round is opened.
ruleModal.list06: Dynamically precipitates into a red pool if the conditions are not met

joinbox.withdrawTip: Tips: click the withdrawal button to withdraw all the withdrawal rewards.

testimonial.t02: There's still time for the next draw
testimonial.info: The Grand Prize Pool will be awarded once every 24 hours. For each new investment, the time will be extended by 3 hours, and 100% of the prize pool will be awarded to the last 500 players with the largest investment. The small prize pool will be awarded once every 24 hours, 1/3 for the first prize, 1/3 for the second prize, and 1/3 for the third prize.
